statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `transactions` left join `users` as `u_from` on `u_from`.`id` = `transactions`.`user_from_id` left join `users` as `u_to` on `u_to`.`id` = `transactions`.`user_to_id` where `user_from_id` = '1' or `user_to_id` = '1'

select `transactions`.*, (
CASE transactions.currency_iso
WHEN u_from.currency_iso
THEN (
SELECT cr.rate
FROM currency_rates cr
WHERE cr.currency_iso = u_from.currency_iso
ORDER BY cr.date DESC
LIMIT 1
)
WHEN u_to.currency_iso
THEN (
SELECT cr.rate
FROM currency_rates cr
WHERE cr.currency_iso = u_to.currency_iso
ORDER BY cr.date DESC
LIMIT 1
)
WHEN "USD" THEN 1
END) as rate from `transactions` left join `users` as `u_from` on `u_from`.`id` = `transactions`.`user_from_id` left join `users` as `u_to` on `u_to`.`id` = `transactions`.`user_to_id` where `user_from_id` = '1' or `user_to_id` = '1' order by `transactions`.`id` asc limit 100 offset 0
